"For convenience, single strings are automatically wrapped in a list "
"internally, so you don't need to write ``expression=[\"[x] * 2\"]`` - "
"just use ``expression=\"[x] * 2\"`` or the even simpler positional form: "
"``Number(\"doubled\", \"[x] * 2\")``."
